snippet.title: Midnight Protocol - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
The official reveal trailer for Midnight Protocol, a tactical narrative-driven RPG in a digital future. Hack into servers, beat security and steal encrypted data in a world where your identity is just another network address.

Available in 2020 on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1162700/Midnight_Protocol/
